nodes.text: The Rushlight Equinox was a starship that existed during the High Republic Era, owned by Vishla. When hyperspace was being reopened after the Great Hyperspace Disaster, the Rushlight Equinox was on Coruscant. Leox Gyasi, a friend of Vishla's who was captain of the Byne Guild ship Vessel, noted the ship's presence when he arrived on Coruscant and hoped to swap stories with Vishla about what her crew had done while grounded.
